  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    This task is applicable to elements with&amp;nbsp;a safety goal that has an&amp;nbsp;ASIL of (B), C and D.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The single point and latent fault metric values specified in the system specification shall be considered when showing&#xD;
    compliance to this item.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    It is recommended that users refer to ISO 26262, volume 5 annexes C, E and F&amp;nbsp;for information regarding HW&#xD;
    architectural metrics.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <purpose>To determine the single point fault and latent fault metrics applicable to the item under development based upon the&#xD;
measures for detection of these sorts of errors described in the system specification.</purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
